OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772572329
OL,3,CDrink driver admits causing death of
OL,4,Cteenage passenger
OL,6,FBouncer only held a provisional
OL,7,Fdriving license and was drink driving.
OL,8,FHe lost control of the car on Wheldon
OL,9,FRoad, causing it to crashed through a
OL,10,Ffence and into a disused water
OL,11,Ftreatment tank belonging to Yorkshire
OL,12,FWater.
OL,14,FThe vehicle's 21-year-old owner
OL,15,Fsuffered serious injuries.
OL,17,FTaylor, a father-of-two, was thrown
OL,18,Ffrom the car. He suffered head
OL,19,Finjuries and died at the scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772572329
OL,3,CDrink driver admits causing death of
OL,4,Cteenage passenger
OL,6,FTaylor's girlfriend, Megan Carswell,
OL,7,Ffound out she was pregnant with his
OL,8,Fsecond child ten days after he died.
OL,10,FShe says she now lives "in a constant
OL,11,Fsense of numbness, fear and disbelief.
OL,12,FOur son will never get chance to meet
OL,13,Fhis daddy, and Taylor will never get
OL,14,Fchance to meet his son.
OL,16,F"Taylor also has a daughter who was 11
OL,17,Fmonths old at the time he was killed.
OL,18,FShe still looks at photos of him and
OL,19,Fpoints and says daddy.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772572329
OL,3,CDrink driver admits causing death of
OL,4,Cteenage passenger
OL,6,F"Taylor's future was stolen from him.
OL,7,FHis chance to watch both his daughter
OL,8,Fand son grow up was taken away by the
OL,9,Fdefendant. This loss is permanent and
OL,10,Fwill follow me and his children for
OL,11,Fthe rest of our lives."
OL,13,FBouncer, who is from Pontefract,
OL,14,Fadmitted causing death by dangerous
OL,15,Fdriving at Leeds Crown Court on Monday
OL,16,F2 March.
OL,18,FHe also admitted causing death while
OL,19,Fdrink driving, causing death while
OL,20,Fdriving uninsured and causing death
OL,21,Fwhile driving without a full licence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772572329
OL,3,CDrink driver admits causing death of
OL,4,Cteenage passenger
OL,6,FHe has been jailed for eight years and
OL,7,Fbanned from driving for 10 years and
OL,8,Ffour months.
OL,10,FTaylor's mum, Gemma Mason, said: "My
OL,11,Fwhole world came crashing down around
OL,12,Fme because of the defendant's careless
OL,13,Factions.
OL,15,F"This moment of stupidity and
OL,16,Fcarelessness has ripped my whole
OL,17,Ffamily apart.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772572329
OL,3,CDrink driver admits causing death of
OL,4,Cteenage passenger
OL,6,F"I cannot put into words how you have
OL,7,Fmade me feel because I can't, there
OL,8,Fisn't enough pages in the world to
OL,9,Fexpress how I am feeling right now."
OL,11,FSpeaking after the sentencing, DS Paul
OL,12,FLightowler said: "This was a
OL,13,Fcompletely avoidable tragedy. A young
OL,14,Flife has been lost because someone
OL,15,Fchose to drive while under the
OL,16,Finfluence of alcohol.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772572329
OL,3,CDrink driver admits causing death of
OL,4,Cteenage passenger
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with Taylor's
OL,7,Ffamily, and we urge everyone to
OL,8,Funderstand that getting behind the
OL,9,Fwheel after drinking carries
OL,10,Fdevastating consequences."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
